Class AbstractVehicle

  • java.lang.Object
    • problem2.AbstractVehicle
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Automobile, Bus, Motorcycle, Truck

    public abstract class AbstractVehicle
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents detailed information of a vehicle, including color, current velocity, max allowed velocity, min allowed velocity, and current direction
